          </h2>
          <p class="text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto" style="color: var(--color-text-secondary); font-family: var(--font-body);">
            Setup takes about an hour. We handle all the technical configuration — your staff and members never notice a thing.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6 mb-14">
